title: ADC/Jungle Main LF Ranked Team (Gold IV)
body:
I'm pretty well coordinated (and 20 years of age), have been in team environments before, both as a leader/shot-caller in game and coach out of game. I have good communication and a broad champion pool on both roles. I can adapt based on team needs. Highest I have been is Plat 5, but I'm down to where I feel more comfortable, but I'm looking to get back into a more competitive setting and hopefully reach the top one day.

Champs I main:  (Jungle)

Lee Sin
Udyr
Malphite
Elise
Nunu
Rengar

(ADC)

Tristana
Vayne
Lucian
Miss fortune
Cait
Twitch
